T1  - COLLATERAL REQUIREMENTS AND ASSET PRICES
AU  - Brumm, Johannes
AU  - Grill, Michael
AU  - Kubler, Felix
AU  - Schmedders, Karl
Y1  - 2015/02/01
PY  - 2015
DA  - 2015/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12092
